Subject: [PATCH C-04] Add SSRF redirect validation and DNS re-resolution

High: SSRF resolve_and_check() doesn't re-resolve DNS before
connection, allowing DNS rebinding attacks. Redirect targets
are not validated.

File: core/ssrf.py

--- a/core/ssrf.py
